<http://dx.doi.org/10.35463/j.apr.2020.01.01>
    bibo:endPage "17" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Acta Palaeontologica Romaniae" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2019-10-25" ;
    bibo:startPage "3" ;
    bibo:volume "16" ;
    dc:creator "Iamandei, Stanila; Iamandei, Eugenia; Stoia, Tiberiu" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Fossil Woods From Bozovici (Sw Romania)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10520710>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10520704> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10520710>
    dc:description "Fig. 6 a-i. (graphic scale, μm). Spiroplatanoxylon densiradiatum (Petrescu) Süss 2007, Bozovici, Romania. a-c. (cross section) – distinct boundary of growth ring, diffuse-porous wood structure, ray dilatations at boundaries. d-f. Tangential section – two-sized rays - fine and multiseriate (d), spiral thickenings on vessels (f). g-i. Radial section – badly preserved scalariform perforation plates (h), round simple pits in cross fields." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10520710/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10520704>
    dc:description "Fig. 3 Two of the studied samples (nos. 27621, 27622)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10520704/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

